# PET Unit Authoring

**Read first:** `scripts/lib/pet-blueprints/TEMPLATE.md`

**Gold reference (Unit 1):** `scripts/lib/pet-blueprints/unit-01/` + `shared/education-and-future-plans-content.mjs`

**Curriculum:** `data/curriculum/cambridge-curriculum-map.json` → `levels.pet.units[N-1]`

## Pipeline

```bash
npm run generate:pet-units -- <N>
npm run validate:pet
npm run generate:listening-audio -- pet <N>
npm run seed:pet -- --from <N> --to <N> --unlock-test-student
```

## PET settings

- `levelTag`: `"pet"`
- Writing `minWords`: 40
- Speaking `maxDurationSeconds`: 150
- Character: **Minh (15)** — education/career arc
- 18 lessons × 90 exercises; AI only on Check
- **No image-based lesson questions** — text-only `sceneDescription`; see `unit-content-authoring.mdc`.
